{"tid":1698630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家今晚早啲訓，聽朝八點準時和你返工，希望可以見到你地","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T16:17:27.000Z","uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c003b9d8186d9f05a0360e41cc6644725142a9ec","tid":1698630,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"1108 和你返工2.0 <br />\n所有路線0745集合 0800準時起步<br />\n<br />\n九龍西集合點<br />\n1. 旺角C4 朗豪坊<br />\n往尖沙咀方向：經彌敦道，到達sogo外解散<br />\n2. 尖沙咀 半島集合 <br />\n往旺角方向，滙豐解散<br />\n3. 楓樹街遊樂場<br />\n往荔枝角，沿長沙灣道，長沙灣廣場解散<br />\n<br />\n九龍東集合點<br />\n1. 九龍灣A<br />\n2. 觀塘A<br />\n雙向行走：經觀塘道<br />\n<br />\n港島區<br />\n<br />\n1. 上環E4<br />\n<br />\n2. 銅鑼灣E（東西雙線）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;雙向行走：經軒尼詩道、金鐘道、德輔道中（以上各為解散地點）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;往太古坊：經英皇道，太古坊解散<br />\n<br />\n3. 太古城（C出口）<br />\n經英皇道，皇仁書院解散<br />\n<br />\n新界東<br />\n1. 大圍A<br />\n2. 沙田新城市近黨鐵站<br />\n雙向行走：經村南道、文禮路、希爾頓、新城市<br />\n（各為解散點）<br />\n<br />\n新界西<br />\n1. 葵芳D <br />\n經興芳路、葵富路、葵涌道，葵興站解散<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gotoworktogether\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgotoworktogether&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=a41bf16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gotoworktogether</a>"},{"pid":"4261621b09dbd057a57caff125cf5c627dfbb618","tid":1698630,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTuN5e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTuN5e2.jpg&h=b95a95f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHkmqe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHkmqe3.jpg&h=2fe775b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e6f02bf0a6d2443d5a3c48cbeec30f10018049c","tid":1698630,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dd6782d4